column1: B&B HOTEL Paris Porte des Lilas
column2: Located in 19th district of Paris, B&B Hôtel Porte des Lilas offers a 24-hour reception, luggage storage and a terrace. Porte des Lilas Metro Station is a 5-minute walk away and offers direct access to the Hôtel de Ville.

Located in Amsterdam, 3.7 km from A'DAM Lookout, Tribe Amsterdam City has accommodations with a fitness center, private parking, a shared lounge and a bar. With free WiFi, this 4-star hotel offers a 24-hour front desk and luggage storage space. Guests can have a drink at the snack bar.
